		(symbol "SlaveSoftware_1_1"
			(text "Cell monitor:\n Setup cell monitor circuit.\n  - Set number of cells to monitor\n  - Set all relevant settings.\n Process cell voltages.\n  - Two stage error if under/over voltage\n  - Soft error if delta exceeds threshold\n Report min/max/average/total voltage to master\nCell balancing\n Monitor cell balancing enable from master and:\n  -Initiate cell balancing if above threshold voltage\n  -Initiate cell balancing if delta threshold exceeded\n  -Override enable if hard overvoltage fault?\n  -Stop balancing when delta is below threshold\n  -Pause balancing if temperature out-of-range\nTemperature monitoring:\n Setup temperature monitoring circuit\n  - Set active temperature sensors\n  - Set relevant ADC settings (local or external?)\n Set calibration for type of sensors used.\n Process temperatures\n  - Two stage error for temperature out-of-range\n  - Error for unreliable sensor reading\n Report min/max/average temperature to master\nCurrent monitoring\n Software enable/disable\n See Master Software block for requirements\nAdditional Master tasks may be included if single module.\n "
